---
---

<section id="hero" class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img
      src="/images/PPh2.webp"
      alt="Pepe Céspedes tocando piano" fetchpriority="high"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover object-top md:object-[center_15%]"
    />

    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-black/60 via-transparent to-black/30"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex min-h-screen items-end md:items-center">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 pb-16 pt-28 sm:px-6 sm:pb-20 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="mb-4 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/70 sm:text-xs">
          Pianista · Compositor
        </p>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl leading-none text-white sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl">
          Pepe Céspedes
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-sm italic text-white/75 sm:text-base">
          "La música es el espacio donde encuentro paz, respuestas, motivación.
          Todo lo que recibo de la música es positivo".
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>